                <div class="content-main right">
                    <h1>Human Resources</h1>
                    
     <div class="interior-bg-1 styled-bg"><div class="container-inner cf">
<div class="full-col flex-col">
    <p>If you&rsquo;re interested in working for a Christian university that is as serious about what you bring to our faith mission as our educational mission, let&rsquo;s talk.&nbsp;Lipscomb is a top-rated southeastern university on the grow that continues to break its own enrollment records every year. As a result, there are usually employment openings at any given time on both the faculty and the staff side both full- and part-time.</p>

<p><img alt="Faculty one-on-one instruction after class." src="/uploads/66024.jpg" style="width: 565px; height: 318px; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid;" /></p>

<p>Salary and benefits are competitive and attractive and, of course, we are located in what is now being called one of the most livable cities in the nation, Nashville, Tenn. Click below in the area of your greatest interest to find out who we are looking for right now to join the Lipscomb family.</p>

<p><a class="button" href="/hr/Staff">Staff</a> <a class="button" href="/hr/Faculty">Faculty</a> <a class="button" href="/hr/Adjunct">Adjunct</a> <a class="button" href="/academy/Page/Index/9918">Lipscomb Academy</a></p>

<h4>Quick Links</h4>

<ul>
	<li><a href="/hr/To-Work-at-Lipscomb">What it means to work at Lipscomb</a></li>
	<li><a href="/hr/Holidays">Campus holidays and closures</a></li>
</ul>

<p><small>Lipscomb University complies with all applicable federal and state nondiscrimination laws and does not engage in prohibited discrimination on the basis of race, religion, sex, age, color, national or ethnic origin or disability in the administration of its employment practices.</small></p>
<p>
</div>

